# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to login to the application

# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to get, create, update, delete the projects my
# employees will work on.

# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to get, create, update, delete the users that will use
# my application.

# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to get, create, update, delete the activity types to
# better classify the hours spent in a project

# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to associate zero or more users to a project to allow
# them to insert hours in that specified project

# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to associate zero or more activity types to a project to
# allow the user to specify what activity did he do in those hours

# ● As an Admin, I want to be able to search timesheets filtering by user, project, activity,
# date range and I do not want to see more than 10 results for each page

# ● As a User, I want to be able to login to the application

# ● As a User, I want to be able to add or update a Timesheet specifying the project
# (among those for which I am allowed), the activity type (among those that are
# available for the project), the date of the activity, the hours spent and a brief
# description for each activity.

# ● As a User, I want to be able to search my timesheets filtering by project, activity, date
# range and I do not want to see more than 10 results for each page